b80ba-74a6-4b9f-9c45-ca663e720454',NULL,'CL_PAR30','PAR 30 (%)','Portfolio at Risk >30 days: outstanding balance of loans 30+ DPD / total portfolio. CGAP standard; CBN MFB target <5%.','credit_lending','percent','lower_better',3.00,'[\"credit\", \"branch\"]','auto','par30',1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14b80ba-7794-482d-87db-0a2de2e5ae11',NULL,'CL_PAR60','PAR 60 (%)','Portfolio at Risk >60 days. Indicates emerging credit quality issues.','credit_lending','percent','lower_better',2.50,'[\"credit\", \"branch\"]','auto','par60',1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14b80ba-7b19-44be-b459-2405fde6952e',NULL,'CL_PAR90','PAR 90 (%)','Portfolio at Risk >90 days. Maps to CBN Substandard + Doubtful + Loss classification bands.','credit_lending','percent','lower_better',3.00,'[\"credit\", \"branch\"]','auto','par90',1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14b80ba-7e3f-4c8f-813e-9c63328cea7f',NULL,'CL_COLLECTION_EFFICIENCY','Collection Efficiency (%)','Repayments received / amounts due in period × 100. CGAP benchmark: >95% for healthy MFB.','credit_lending','percent','higher_better',3.00,'[\"credit\", \"collections\", \"branch\"]','auto','collection_efficiency',1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14b80ba-80f1-4414-aadd-bc9473df2fd7',NULL,'CL_DISBURSEMENT_TAT','Disbursement TAT (days)','Average days from loan application to disbursement. Lower = faster service delivery.','credit_lending','days','lower_better',1.50,'[\"credit\"]','auto','disbursement_tat',1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14b80ba-83f3-400d-967b-86491908b152',NULL,'CL_WRITE_OFF_RATIO','Write-off Ratio (%)','Total loans written off / total portfolio × 100. CBN Prudential Guidelines metric.','credit_lending','percent','lower_better',2.00,'[\"credit\", \"branch\"]','manual',NULL,1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14b80ba-86ca-452e-afcf-ecd72fdf263e',NULL,'CL_LOAN_RENEWAL_RATE','Loan Renewal Rate (%)','Percentage of closed loans that were renewed/reborrowed by the same customer. CGAP sustainability metric.','credit_lending','percent','higher_better',1.00,'[\"credit\"]','manual',NULL,1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14b80ba-895b-487b-bf11-7d15de898dcf',NULL,'OPS_TXN_VOLUME','Transactions Processed (Count)','Total number of transactions processed by the officer/branch in the period.','operations','count','higher_better',1.00,'[\"operations\", \"branch\"]','manual',NULL,1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14b80ba-8ca0-45a9-b75b-85cca4481981',NULL,'OPS_KYC_COMPLETION','KYC Completion Rate (%)','Percentage of customers with fully completed KYC documentation. CBN KYC Circular requirement.','operations','percent','higher_better',1.50,'[\"operations\", \"compliance\", \"branch\"]','manual',NULL,1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14b80ba-8fa4-4fc9-ae78-29a0dc3c1e36',NULL,'OPS_SLA_COMPLIANCE','Workflow SLA Compliance (%)','Percentage of workflows/tasks completed within SLA deadlines.','operations','percent','higher_better',1.00,'[\"operations\"]','manual',NULL,1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14b80ba-9261-4aae-a321-43ad215a2978',NULL,'OPS_ERROR_RATE','Error / Reversal Rate (%)','Percentage of transactions reversed or corrected. Basel III operational risk indicator.','operations','percent','lower_better',1.00,'[\"operations\"]','manual',NULL,1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14b80ba-9574-4254-a600-cc2af5b64897',NULL,'CS_COMPLAINTS_RESOLVED','Complaints Resolved (%)','Percentage of customer complaints resolved in the period. CBN Consumer Protection Framework.','customer_service','percent','higher_better',1.50,NULL,'manual',NULL,1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14b80ba-9864-4ec1-a36c-a8764e0bef2c',NULL,'CS_COMPLAINT_TAT','Complaint Resolution TAT (days)','Average days to resolve a customer complaint. CBN mandates ≤2 business days.','customer_service','days','lower_better',1.50,NULL,'manual',NULL,1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14b80ba-9afd-402a-8607-a11ac1762372',NULL,'CS_SATISFACTION_SCORE','Customer Satisfaction Score','Average customer satisfaction rating (1–5 scale). CGAP outreach metric.','customer_service','score','higher_better',1.00,NULL,'manual',NULL,1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14b80ba-9dde-4eb2-bc35-cde62e908cd0',NULL,'BR_LOAN_PORTFOLIO','Branch Loan Portfolio (₦)','Total outstanding loan balance for the branch. CBN branch-level return metric.','branch','ngn','higher_better',2.00,'[\"branch\"]','manual',NULL,1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14b80ba-a0bb-4c1a-9304-870a9e5cd2b1',NULL,'BR_DEPOSIT_PORTFOLIO','Branch Deposit Portfolio (₦)','Total deposit liabilities of the branch.','branch','ngn','higher_better',2.00,'[\"branch\"]','manual',NULL,1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14b80ba-a374-4371-ba23-dfb82a3ff856',NULL,'BR_OSS','Operational Self-Sufficiency (%)','Financial revenue / total operating expense × 100. CGAP: >100% = financially viable branch.','branch','percent','higher_better',2.00,'[\"branch\"]','manual',NULL,1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14b80ba-a65b-44d2-b34c-aad37eb9206e',NULL,'BR_STAFF_PRODUCTIVITY','Staff Productivity (Loans/Officer)','Average number of active loans per credit officer in the branch. CGAP benchmark: >100 per officer.','branch','count','higher_better',1.00,'[\"branch\"]','manual',NULL,1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14b80ba-a939-4230-b5ad-e78744292ae8',NULL,'BR_NEW_CUSTOMERS','New Customers Acquired','Number of new customers onboarded by the branch in the period.','branch','count','higher_better',1.50,'[\"branch\", \"marketing\"]','manual',NULL,1,1,'2026-03-14 01:49:03','2026-03-14 01:49:03'),('a14f5689-76d0-420a-ab20-5692d105e986','a14a96f2-006d-4232-973e-9683ef578737','KPI-LOAN-001','Loan Disbursement Volume','Total value of loans disbursed in the period','credit_lending','currency','hig