unt Disbursed: NGN 100,000.00\nNew Combined Principal: NGN 401,700.40\nNew Interest Rate: 3.50%\nNew Tenure: 10 months\nDisbursement Account: 1000000888\n\nYour previous loan has been closed and replaced by the new loan above.\n\nRegards,\nDemo Microfinance Bank','sent','sent:ok','2026-03-13 16:07:34','2026-03-13 16:07:33','2026-03-13 16:07:34'),('a14ab222-1cee-4244-a820-bd3e62495004','a14a96f2-006d-4232-973e-9683ef578737','a14a986c-ce88-4272-8b44-f54c405c4e1f','sms','08034567890','deposit_received','Credit Alert: NGN 250,000.00 deposited to 1001234567 on 13 Mar 2026, 5:11pm. Desc: Cash Deposit at Victoria Island Branch. Bal: NGN 1,250,000.00. Ref: TRX-TESTPREVIEW1. - Demo MFB','sent','simulated:ok','2026-03-13 16:11:22','2026-03-13 16:11:22','2026-03-13 16:11:22'),('a14ab222-2673-4b4f-8325-0937ed901548','a14a96f2-006d-4232-973e-9683ef578737','a14a986c-ce88-4272-8b44-f54c405c4e1f','email','adaeze.okafor@gmail.com','deposit_received','Dear Adaeze Okafor,\n\nYour account has been credited.\n\nAmount: NGN 250,000.00\nAccount: 1001234567\nDescription: Cash Deposit at Victoria Island Branch\nTransaction Ref: TRX-TESTPREVIEW1\nDate: 13 Mar 2026, 5:11pm\nNew Balance: NGN 1,250,000.00\n\nIf you did not authorise this transaction, please contact us immediately.\n\nRegards,\nDemo Microfinance Bank','sent','sent:ok','2026-03-13 16:11:22','2026-03-13 16:11:22','2026-03-13 16:11:22'),('a14ab2cc-7801-4c8e-bf5c-17d4ae983bfd','a14a96f2-006d-4232-973e-9683ef578737','a14a98a7-7496-4a08-84ec-6fc9147bf945','sms','09012345678','loan_topup_approved','Dear Seun Adeyemi, your loan top-up of NGN 120,000.00 has been approved. New loan LNF-GY7DYYON7W-T1-T1 (NGN 521,700.40, 10 months) created. - Demo MFB','sent','simulated:ok','2026-03-13 16:13:13','2026-03-13 16:13:13','2026-03-13 16:13:13'),('a14ab2cc-88b9-43ff-b622-730d0f6a5a28','a14a96f2-006d-4232-973e-9683ef578737','a14a98a7-7496-4a08-84ec-6fc9147bf945','email','seun.adeyemi@gmail.com','loan_topup_approved','Dear Seun Adeyemi,\n\nYour loan top-up request has been approved and funds have been credited to your account.\n\nNew Loan Reference: LNF-GY7DYYON7W-T1-T1\nTop-up Amount Disbursed: NGN 120,000.00\nNew Combined Principal: NGN 521,700.40\nNew Interest Rate: 3.50%\nNew Tenure: 10 months\nDisbursement Account: 1000000888\n\nYour previous loan has been closed and replaced by the new loan above.\n\nRegards,\nDemo Microfinance Bank','sent','sent:ok','2026-03-13 16:13:14','2026-03-13 16:13:14','2026-03-13 16:13:14'),('a14ab324-5340-44c5-826f-d285a2950180','a14a96f2-006d-4232-973e-9683ef578737','a14a98a7-487f-4df6-8b71-8f7560071838','sms','07034567891','deposit_received','Credit Alert: NGN 500,000.00 deposited to 1000000666 on 13 Mar 2026, 5:14pm. Desc: Main cash deposit. Bal: NGN 3,180,000.00. Ref: TRX-LMI0AXRDL4. - Demo MFB','sent','simulated:ok','2026-03-13 16:14:11','2026-03-13 16:14:11','2026-03-13 16:14:11'),('a14ab324-678b-407b-bd1f-1899c41d9056','a14a96f2-006d-4232-973e-9683ef578737','a14a98a7-487f-4df6-8b71-8f7560071838','email','ibrahim.aliyu@mail.com','deposit_received','Dear Ibrahim Aliyu,\n\nYour account has been credited.\n\nAmount: NGN 500,000.00\nAccount: 1000000666\nDescription: Main cash deposit\nTransaction Ref: TRX-LMI0AXRDL4\nDate: 13 Mar 2026, 5:14pm\nNew Balance: NGN 3,180,000.00\n\nIf you did not authorise this transaction, please contact us immediately.\n\nRegards,\nDemo Microfinance Bank','sent','sent:ok','2026-03-13 16:14:11','2026-03-13 16:14:11','2026-03-13 16:14:11'),('a14be0a5-33c0-4a05-b936-002b75b40107','a14a96f2-006d-4232-973e-9683ef578737','a14acc23-2050-4c6e-a2d9-bcc5f3e86d18','sms','+23481-100-2004','deposit_received','Credit Alert: NGN 8,000,000.00 deposited to 1008941146 on 14 Mar 2026, 7:17am. Desc: loan to my self. Bal: NGN 8,079,370.00. Ref: TRX-K8LUUTUHZI. - Demo MFB','sent','simulated:ok','2026-03-14 06:17:15','2026-03-14 06:17:15','2026-03-14 06:17:15');
